      <title class="- topic/title ">
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">22.2110</ph> Contract clause.</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body concept/conbody ">
         <p id="d1529e8" class="- topic/p ">Insert the clause at <xref href="52.222-62.dita#FAR_52_222_62"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref ">52.222-62</xref>, Paid Sick Leave Under Executive Order 13706, in solicitations and contracts that include the clause at <xref href="52.222-6.dita#FAR_52_222_6"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref ">52.222-6</xref>, Construction Wage Rate Requirements, or <xref href="52.222-41.dita#FAR_52_222_41"
                  outputclass="fm:ParaNumOnly"
                  class="- topic/xref ">52.222-41</xref>, Service Contract Labor Standards, where work is to be performed, in whole or in part, in the United States (the 50 States and the District of Columbia).</p>
